---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="FluxLinux OS — Overview">
    <div class="relative bg-white dark:bg-dark py-24 sm:py-32 overflow-hidden">
        <div
            class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-white dark:from-slate-900 dark:to-dark -z-10"
        >
        </div>

        <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl lg:mx-0">
                <p class="text-base font-semibold leading-7 text-primary">
                    FluxLinux OS
                </p>
                <h1
                    class="mt-2 text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 dark:text-white sm:text-6xl"
                >
                    A distro that stays out of your way.
                </h1>
                <p
                    class="mt-6 text-lg leading-8 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300"
                >
                    FluxLinux ships a clean desktop, fast boot, and a toolchain
                    that doesn’t feel like an afterthought. It’s designed for
                    people who like control — but also like sleeping.
                </p>
                <div class="mt-10 flex items-center gap-x-6">
                    <a
                        href="/os/download/"
                        class="rounded-md bg-primary px-3.5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-primary-hover focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-primary transition-colors"
                        >Get FluxLinux</a
                    >
                    <a
                        href="/help/"
                        class="text-sm font-semibold leading-6 text-gray-900 dark:text-white"
                        >Learn more <span aria-hidden="true">→</span></a
                    >
                </div>
            </div>

            <div
                class="mx-auto mt-16 grid max-w-2xl grid-cols-1 gap-x-8 gap-y-16 lg:mx-0 lg:mt-10 lg:max-w-none lg:grid-cols-12"
            >
                <div class="lg:col-span-12 lg:grid lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-8">
                    <!-- Highlights -->
                    <div
                        class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-slate-800/50 rounded-2xl p-8 ring-1 ring-gray-200 dark:ring-gray-700"
                    >
                        <h3
                            class="text-lg font-semibold leading-8 text-gray-900 dark:text-white"
                        >
                            Highlights
                        </h3>
                        <ul
                            role="list"
                            class="mt-6 space-y-4 text-base leading-7 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300"
                        >
                            <li class="flex gap-x-3">
                                <svg
                                    class="h-6 w-5 flex-none text-primary"
                                    viewBox="0 0 20 20"
                                    fill="currentColor"
                                    aria-hidden="true"
                                    ><path
                                        fill-rule="evenodd"
                                        d="M16.704 4.153a.75.75 0 01.143 1.052l-8 10.5a.75.75 0 01-1.127.075l-4.5-4.5a.75.75 0 011.06-1.06l3.894 3.893 7.48-9.817a.75.75 0 011.05-.143z"
                                        clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg
                                >
                                Fast boot and snappy desktop interactions
                            </li>
                            <li class="flex gap-x-3">
                                <svg
                                    class="h-6 w-5 flex-none text-primary"
                                    viewBox="0 0 20 20"
                                    fill="currentColor"
                                    aria-hidden="true"
                                    ><path
                                        fill-rule="evenodd"
                                        d="M16.704 4.153a.75.75 0 01.143 1.052l-8 10.5a.75.75 0 01-1.127.075l-4.5-4.5a.75.75 0 011.06-1.06l3.894 3.893 7.48-9.817a.75.75 0 011.05-.143z"
                                        clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg
                                >
                                Curated defaults with sensible power-user options
                            </li>
                            <li class="flex gap-x-3">
                                <svg
                                    class="h-6 w-5 flex-none text-primary"
                                    viewBox="0 0 20 20"
                                    fill="currentColor"
                                    aria-hidden="true"
                                    ><path
                                        fill-rule="evenodd"
                                        d="M16.704 4.153a.75.75 0 01.143 1.052l-8 10.5a.75.75 0 01-1.127.075l-4.5-4.5a.75.75 0 011.06-1.06l3.894 3.893 7.48-9.817a.75.75 0 011.05-.143z"
                                        clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg
                                >
                                Modern package workflow
                            </li>
                            <li class="flex gap-x-3">
                                <svg
                                    class="h-6 w-5 flex-none text-primary"
                                    viewBox="0 0 20 20"
                                    fill="currentColor"
                                    aria-hidden="true"
                                    ><path
                                        fill-rule="evenodd"
                                        d="M16.704 4.153a.75.75 0 01.143 1.052l-8 10.5a.75.75 0 01-1.127.075l-4.5-4.5a.75.75 0 011.06-1.06l3.894 3.893 7.48-9.817a.75.75 0 011.05-.143z"
                                        clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg
                                >
                                Privacy-respecting telemetry: off by default
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Requirements -->
                    <div
                        class="mt-8 lg:mt-0 bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-2xl p-8 ring-1 ring-gray-200 dark:ring-gray-700 shadow-sm"
                    >
                        <h3
                            class="text-lg font-semibold leading-8 text-gray-900 dark:text-white"
                        >
                            System Requirements
                        </h3>
                        <p
                            class="mt-2 text-base leading-7 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400"
                        >
                            Targeting modest hardware while still feeling
                            modern.
                        </p>
                        <dl
                            class="mt-6 space-y-4 text-base leading-7 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300"
                        >
                            <div class="flex gap-x-3">
                                <dt
                                    class="font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white w-20"
                                >
                                    CPU
                                </dt>
                                <dd>64-bit dual-core</dd>
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex gap-x-3">
                                <dt
                                    class="font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white w-20"
                                >
                                    RAM
                                </dt>
                                <dd>4 GB (8 GB recommended)</dd>
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex gap-x-3">
                                <dt
                                    class="font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white w-20"
                                >
                                    Storage
                                </dt>
                                <dd>20 GB+</dd>
                            </div>
                        </dl>
                        <div class="mt-6">
                            <a
                                href="/help/"
                                class="text-sm font-semibold leading-6 text-primary hover:text-primary-hover"
                                >See full details <span aria-hidden="true"
                                    >→</span
                                ></a
                            >
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</Layout>
